Lost Cavern
A quest for priceless treasures

by Simon Richards

Welcome to the Lost Cavern adventure.
You have travelled many days to explore where, legend has it, a series of caverns filled with treasures have been undisturbed for centuries.
Many others have searched the wilderness but no-one has ever found the lost cavern or its treasures.

To track your progress type SCORE.
For information about playing type HELP.
Good luck!

